  • Constructor Details

    • BotManager

      public BotManager(int autoRespawnDelay, boolean hasGravity, InetSocketAddress inetAddr, @Nullable @Nullable String nickPath, @Nullable @Nullable String nickPrefix)
      Create an instance of bot manager
      Parameters:
      autoRespawnDelay - Delay for auto-respawning (0 = instant, -1 = never)
      hasGravity - Whether the bots have gravity
      inetAddr - Address to connect bots to (see Utils.createInetAddress(String, int))
      nickPath - Path for nickname file (if null will generate from built in file)
      nickPrefix - Prefix for nicknames
